---
title: Halifax Style Donairs with Garlic Sauce and Spring Mix Salad
description: A truly delicious East Coast classic, this version of the famed donair will definitely excite the taste buds. The pepper beef wrapped with fresh vegetables and sweet garlic sauce may just have you wishing you were in Sherbrooke right now!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/donair-style-halifax-78365a68.jpg
